process_notes: EPSG:4326,EPSG:4267,EPSG:4269 We used updated GAP files and added them to the Protected Area Dataset. There was some error in the additions because of the slight difference in projections. Some polygons may appear to have a border around an edge because of the difference in projections. We tried to manually delete these excess borders of the overlays as much as possible.

description: ArcIMS 9.3.0 Web Map Service for the Southeast Watershed Forum. This data was compiled to have an updated and comprehensive look at the protected areas of the southeast. Initially, it will be used in a web-based mapping application, but has a wide range of utility.
